content: Ryan Gallagher announced he was joining OnlyFans on Thursday.

But in a crushing blow for the MAFS star, his paywalled content has been leaked online less than one week after launching his account.Several of Ryan's explicit images and videos have been published on a notorious online porn forum, reports Yahoo Lifestyle.An industry expert said this could result in the 34-year-old 'losing tens of thousands of dollars in revenue' from OnlyFans.The leaked images show Ryan posing completely nude in the shower.

Ryan declared last week he was joining OnlyFans after thinking about it for years.'It's been four years of, "Nah, don't think I will." Well, I did,' he said on Wednesday.For $15 per month, fans can now see a side of Ryan they haven't seen on TV.The bio of Ryan's OnlyFans profile states: 'Just an Aussie bloke with a big willy.'He extended a warm welcome to fans of all backgrounds, genders and body types, but warned against 'flogs' sharing his paid-for content without his permission.Ryan's move into adult work comes after he proposed to Olympian Emily Seebohm.

The couple, who met on set of The Challenge Australia last August, announced their engagement in March.But swimmer Emily, 30, later revealed Ryan had actually popped the question in December, just four months after they met.She told The Daily Telegraph they managed to keep their relationship private for a long time and only went public a day before they got engaged on December 5, 2022.
'We just wanted to live in our own little bubble, we just wanted that for us and our families,' she said.
